{"tid":1334862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重要)關於有人提出臨時政府建議","createTime":"2019-07-20T09:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T11:09:29.000Z","uid":110123,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e75d37cddc999b94025c0ceb4d7e900a07b3deed","tid":1334862,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:33:00.000Z","msg":"建立一個無約束力既政府, 唔好話中國, 根本歐美其他列強都唔會承認, <br />\n之前加泰隆尼亞獨立已經有板你睇, <br />\n而且你單方面宣佈獨立, 等同向干涉國家主權問題, 將會為香港帶來災難<br />\n<br />\n拜訪大家, 我地要既係<span style=\"color: brown;\">五大訴求</span>,最重要係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2020雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國際不承認 加泰隆尼亞獨立將淪空包彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201710280043.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201710280043.aspx&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=0d4e4d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201710280043.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n設在海牙的艾塞爾研究所（Asser Institute）研究員伊蒂利茲（Narin Idriz）認為，若加泰隆尼亞成為獨立國家，相關意涵「不能被低估」。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所有歐盟成員國都珍視自身領土完整，不會希望相同的事發生於國內，加泰隆尼亞想獲任何支持都將非常困難</span></span>。」"},{"pid":"23e8c5df4ee0a4227c57b946ecd4e35e5da4d800","tid":1334862,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af70eef79919e2cfa878ba54b3c4d07558873542","tid":1334862,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[沙盤推演] 大家有無諗過呢場抗爭既end game係點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e77fda5a1834c55703b8f1a1564621bf65f8aec7","tid":1334862,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi